WEBVTT

00:14:56.671 --> 00:15:00.445
a problem not of these large,
impersonal forces.

00:15:02.366 --> 00:15:06.518
We face a problem
of your and my relations.

00:15:07.815 --> 00:15:10.953
We chose ways of relating to each other

00:15:12.345 --> 00:15:13.496
that got us here.

00:15:13.896 --> 00:15:16.645
We can choose ways of relating

00:15:16.669 --> 00:15:18.275
that get us out.

00:15:19.361 --> 00:15:22.630
But there are things
we might have to let go of,

00:15:23.418 --> 00:15:24.599
fellow citizen,

00:15:25.674 --> 00:15:31.280
starting with our own cherished
versions of reality.